text.text: Hotel is good, since no other better options available in the city, however the hotel doesn't serve meal. For food you need to go nearby restaurants. The hotel only arranges Tea, Coffee, Milk and biscuits and for that you have to pay additionally. Nothing is complementary here. Room tariff is nominal. The Location of the hotel is prime, all roads are well connected from the hotel location. The Rules of the hotel administration are strict, the management put a list of rules in the room, of do'es and don'ts.. it's my second time visit in this hotel, overall experience is good 👍.

text.text: I am giving four stars for the place provided standard service despite being in such a locality. Gazetted officers and other office bearers stay here and the hotel provides facilities accordingly. I have deducted 1 star for the unavailability of online or card payment options which can easily be arranged. Have been here previously too and experienced the same kind of facilities at the same price. Advising to book in advance as other places will not offer even half the quality.
